WEBVTT

00:00:15.160 --> 00:00:15.900
Today

00:00:16.699 --> 00:00:18.679
The final battle of the Seven Veins Championship

00:00:19.519 --> 00:00:22.960
Fu Cangtian versus Chen Yuanqi

00:00:23.679 --> 00:00:28.960
The champion will become the Righteous Alliance Leader

00:00:45.740 --> 00:00:46.700
Spirit Hound Elixir

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:49.600
And you still deny it’s you

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:54.159
You’re the mastermind behind the massacre of the Spirit Hound clan

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:57.780
So what if it’s me? What can you do about it?

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:04.200
A noble clan committing such a vicious act

00:01:04.799 --> 00:01:07.879
The strong prey on the weak—this is the Heavenly Way

00:01:08.780 --> 00:01:12.079
Once I win, great scholars will defend my actions

00:01:12.579 --> 00:01:17.400
Only those who survive have the right to talk about honor

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:22.859
After this, everyone will remember me as the Righteous Alliance Leader

00:01:23.239 --> 00:01:26.200
No one will care what I’ve done

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:30.700
A general’s rise is built on countless bones

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:36.200
The weak are only fit to be the mud beneath the strong

00:01:36.599 --> 00:01:39.060
This is the Heavenly Way

00:01:41.159 --> 00:01:41.959
Understand?

00:01:42.700 --> 00:01:43.560
Insects

00:01:44.859 --> 00:01:48.140
But insects have never been wiped out

00:01:49.319 --> 00:01:49.980
Isn’t that right?

00:01:52.799 --> 00:01:53.939
What nonsense are you spouting?

00:01:54.780 --> 00:01:55.939
An ant can try to shake a tree

00:01:56.680 --> 00:01:58.040
A spark will ignite a prairie fire

00:01:58.760 --> 00:02:01.680
Are kings and nobles born superior?

00:02:03.099 --> 00:02:05.480
My fate is not yours to decide

00:02:06.500 --> 00:02:08.219
Screw your so-called Heavenly Way

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:10.699
I only believe in my own path

00:02:20.620 --> 00:02:23.020
You’ve been hiding quite a bit of strength

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:25.199
Likewise

00:03:00.039 --> 00:03:01.280
I will not lose.

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:03.639
I won't lose.

00:03:19.199 --> 00:03:20.020
How could this happen?

00:03:20.240 --> 00:03:21.060
What's going on?

00:03:22.439 --> 00:03:25.099
Why is my spiritual energy backlashing?

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:26.300
Fu Cangtian.

00:03:26.620 --> 00:03:29.780
The spiritual energy in your body comes from the Spirit Hound clan.

00:03:29.979 --> 00:03:33.840
Of course, the Spirit Hound clan can use their bloodline to cause backlash.

00:03:34.460 --> 00:03:35.360
Jiang Yumeng.

00:03:36.099 --> 00:03:36.560
You...

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:42.400
Clan Leader, Jiang Yumeng is here to rescue someone.

00:03:42.639 --> 00:03:44.060
Even with my guards, I couldn't stop her.

00:03:45.680 --> 00:03:46.699
Fu Cangtian.

00:03:47.259 --> 00:03:49.180
For your own selfish gain,

00:03:49.439 --> 00:03:52.759
you stole my golden core bloodline and killed my clansmen.

00:03:53.699 --> 00:03:55.439
You committed heinous crimes.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:00.000
My survival is living proof.

00:04:00.800 --> 00:04:02.900
I never thought Fu Cangtian could be so cruel.

00:04:03.099 --> 00:04:04.759
He is utterly heartless.

00:04:06.800 --> 00:04:09.400
We even thought he was a righteous leader before.

00:04:09.580 --> 00:04:12.159
Turns out he's just a beast in human skin.

00:04:12.539 --> 00:04:14.759
Beast! Beast! Damn beast!

00:04:15.599 --> 00:04:15.960
You...

00:04:17.220 --> 00:04:20.060
You... You're talking nonsense!

00:04:20.220 --> 00:04:24.439
I am the true Righteous Alliance Leader and head of the noble families!

00:04:24.759 --> 00:04:25.980
I am!

00:04:27.660 --> 00:04:28.579
I am!

00:04:31.839 --> 00:04:32.560
Examiner.

00:04:33.339 --> 00:04:38.040
Shouldn't we announce the final result of the Seven Veins Championship?

00:04:38.879 --> 00:04:39.360
Yes.

00:04:42.139 --> 00:04:43.160
I hereby announce,

00:04:44.060 --> 00:04:45.459
the Seven Veins Championship,

00:04:46.220 --> 00:04:47.920
the final champion is

00:04:48.819 --> 00:04:50.259
Chen Yuanqi.

00:04:51.220 --> 00:04:56.199
He will be the Righteous Alliance Leader for the next five years.

00:04:58.939 --> 00:05:00.139
I knew it would be him.

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:31.220
The Divine Sword Ye Clan fully supports Leader Chen Yuanqi.

00:05:31.660 --> 00:05:32.379
Leader Chen.

00:05:32.740 --> 00:05:33.779
Previously, it was our clan leader.

00:05:34.579 --> 00:05:35.079
No, that's not right.

00:05:35.379 --> 00:05:38.259
It was the despicable Fu Cangtian and his son Fu Qingyun.

00:05:38.259 --> 00:05:39.579
They failed to recognize greatness.

00:05:39.660 --> 00:05:41.139
We hope you won't hold our mistakes against us.

00:05:41.139 --> 00:05:42.139
Please spare the Fu family.

00:05:42.480 --> 00:05:44.560
We are willing to compensate with all our clan's resources.

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:45.959
Yes, Leader Chen.

00:05:46.420 --> 00:05:48.459
From now on, you are the honored clan leader of the Yang family.

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:50.040
We will fully support you.

00:05:50.139 --> 00:05:50.759
Shameless!

00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:52.860
The rotten upper beam makes the lower beam crooked.

00:05:54.740 --> 00:05:56.040
My foundation is still unstable.

00:05:56.639 --> 00:05:57.759
If pushed too hard,

00:05:58.199 --> 00:05:59.319
I'm afraid they'll fight like cornered beasts.

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:09.819
Everyone,

00:06:10.860 --> 00:06:12.500
since you honor me as Alliance Leader,

00:06:12.959 --> 00:06:13.779
then today,

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:16.420
I will issue my first order as Alliance Leader.

00:06:17.800 --> 00:06:18.259
Fu family,

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:21.139
you will give half your assets and spiritual medicines

00:06:21.740 --> 00:06:23.199
to compensate the Spirit Hound clan.

00:06:24.100 --> 00:06:24.699
This matter

00:06:25.540 --> 00:06:27.199
will be overseen by the Divine Sword Ye Clan.

00:06:27.899 --> 00:06:28.459
Yang family,

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:31.060
donate half your assets

00:06:31.860 --> 00:06:33.800
to establish schools and relay stations.

00:06:34.620 --> 00:06:37.540
So that the poor across the land have a chance to learn.

00:06:39.139 --> 00:06:42.319
I hope they all have a chance to rise.

00:06:43.819 --> 00:06:46.459
This will be overseen by the Jiang family.

00:06:49.160 --> 00:06:49.720
What do you say?

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:51.639
Thank you for your great virtue, Alliance Leader.

00:06:51.860 --> 00:06:53.459
We will obey your command.

00:07:06.779 --> 00:07:08.259
The Righteous Alliance Leader has been decided.

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:10.740
The Soul Jade has flown here from the Jiang family.

00:07:11.180 --> 00:07:12.480
It is about to recognize its master.

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:15.120
Kid, this is what you deserve.

00:07:17.339 --> 00:07:19.980
I didn't expect you to truly defy fate and succeed.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:21.660
You are indeed my disciple.

00:07:22.180 --> 00:07:24.040
Now that you have the Soul Jade,

00:07:24.180 --> 00:07:25.480
follow me to seal the incantation.

00:07:32.420 --> 00:07:33.259
Power to defy the heavens.

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:35.040
Guide the spirit home.

00:07:35.759 --> 00:07:36.720
Reverse yin and yang.

00:07:37.339 --> 00:07:38.519
Let the soul return to its homeland.

00:07:38.779 --> 00:07:39.740
With my will,

00:07:40.379 --> 00:07:41.360
summon my mother's spirit.

00:07:41.959 --> 00:07:43.040
Cycle of life and death.

00:07:43.699 --> 00:07:45.259
Return to the mortal world.

00:07:55.899 --> 00:07:56.459
Mother.

00:07:58.160 --> 00:07:59.740
Mother! Yuanqi!

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:01.439
Mother.

00:08:03.100 --> 00:08:04.180
Yuanqi! Mother!

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:12.620
Mother cannot speak in the Divine Sword realm.

00:08:12.959 --> 00:08:14.939
But I can see everything clearly.

00:08:16.360 --> 00:08:17.959
To save me,

00:08:19.439 --> 00:08:21.319
you have suffered so much.

00:08:21.660 --> 00:08:23.000
I know it all.

00:08:24.459 --> 00:08:25.639
I know everything.

00:08:26.639 --> 00:08:27.339
Mother.

00:08:28.860 --> 00:08:29.540
Mother.

00:08:35.679 --> 00:08:36.799
Yuanqi

00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:40.100
I know I was wrong.

00:08:41.179 --> 00:08:43.179
I'll do anything you ask.

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:45.419
Can I stay by your side?

00:08:47.159 --> 00:08:47.879
Rouge

00:08:48.519 --> 00:08:49.779
You've committed countless evil deeds.

00:08:50.200 --> 00:08:51.740
And you still dare to ask for forgiveness.

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:54.259
Brother Yuanqi

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:56.639
Is it really impossible?

00:09:01.100 --> 00:09:01.879
Leave.

00:09:02.639 --> 00:09:03.919
Don't ever show up again.

00:09:10.860 --> 00:09:12.340
I gave you a chance.

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:14.059
You forced me.

00:09:23.220 --> 00:09:24.879
Blood Demon Seal, a demonic cult technique.

00:09:25.259 --> 00:09:27.019
You actually dared to practice such forbidden arts.

00:09:28.220 --> 00:09:30.919
This technique will cost you fifty years of lifespan.

00:09:32.019 --> 00:09:34.700
Who did you seal, exactly?